=acts_as_messageable

private messaging plugin for rails.


===installation:

    script/plugin install http://actsasmessageable.googlecode.com/svn/tags/acts_as_messageable-1.0.0
    script/generate messageable
    rake db:migrate


===usage:

    add 'acts_as_messageable' to your user model


